# 📖 Overview

Query Arena is a gamified SQL learning platform designed to make database learning engaging and interactive.

Instead of memorizing SQL syntax, users solve progressively difficult challenges, earn XP, unlock achievements, and climb the leaderboard.

The project combines modern web technologies with an interactive gaming experience to encourage hands-on SQL practice.

---

# 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Secure User Authentication
- 👤 User Profiles
- 🎯 SQL Coding Challenges
- ⚡ Experience Points (XP) System
- 🏅 Achievement Progression
- 📊 Real-time Progress Tracking
- 🧩 Incremental SQL Learning
- 💾 PostgreSQL (Supabase) Integration
- 🎨 Modern Responsive UI
- 🌙 Dark Theme Interface

---

# 🎮 Learning Flow

Each challenge follows an incremental learning approach.

```
Challenge
     │
     ▼
Read Instructions
     │
     ▼
Create Table
     │
     ▼
Insert Data
     │
     ▼
Execute SQL Query
     │
     ▼
Validation
     │
     ▼
Earn XP
     │
     ▼
Unlock Next Challenge
```

---

# 📚 SQL Topics Covered

Current implementation includes:

- SELECT
- WHERE
- ORDER BY
- GROUP BY
- JOIN
- Aggregate Functions
- Constraints
- Primary Keys
- Foreign Keys
- Subqueries

More challenges can easily be added through Supabase.

