# 🏅 XP System

Successful completion of challenges rewards players with Experience Points.

Examples:

| Challenge | XP |
|------------|----|
| SELECT Basics | 50 |
| WHERE Clause | 75 |
| JOIN Challenge | 100 |
| GROUP BY | 120 |
| Subquery | 150 |

